🩺 Cancer Stage Classification & Survival Prediction


 🎯 Use Case
- **Classification**: Predict cancer stage (Stage I, II, III)  
- **Regression**: Predict survival days based on clinical, lifestyle, and treatment variables  
- **Business Development**: Proof-of-concept GenAI pipelines for hospitals, insurers, and startups  
- **Research**: Benchmark dataset for cancer analytics and survival modeling  



I have built a **millions-record cancer dataset** for India — designed for **classification (Stage I, II, III)** and **regression (survival days)**.  
This isn’t just data. It’s a **research accelerator**:  
- Hospitals → Predict patient outcomes  
- Insurers → Risk stratification  
- Startups → GenAI proof-of-concepts  
- Researchers → Benchmark datasets for cancer analytics  

